Welcome to Erthos
@match necromancer
The necromancer's tower is heavily
defended. It would be to hard to fight
those tough guards. Maybe there is
another way.
@match other way
Yes,come to think of it,there is
another way in. But I do not know
exactly where. There was an elf in Dun
Tillok who got in once,but he
dissapeared. He was looking for some
kind of legendary stone of earth. We
have never had such a stone. Maybe we
should find him.
