arch dwarf_priest
name the Dwarven King
msg
@match *
Welcome to my Kingdom!
What is your desire?
@match treasure|adventure|quest
Ahhh...
You wish for an adventure. Well you've
come to the right place! My kingdom is
under threat because of the Necromancer
who lives in the Dark Tower southwest
of here. Many of my subjects have been
kidnapped during the night. I know that
this is the Necromancer's doing. I want
you to slay him and his fabled Dark
Behemoth. You may keep any treasure you
find. This quest shall be a hard one.
Do you wish for help in this quest?
@match yes|Yes
My captain of the guards and my royal
magician shall help you. I hear it
will be extremely hard to break in the
tower,the enterance is heavely guarded
with fierce undead warriors.
Perhaps,you should visit the town of
Dun Tillok for clues.
endmsg
hp 500
x 10
y 1
